C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEven%20the%20dummy%20typing%20this%20imagined%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20imagine%20was%20that%20the%20divorce%20between%20two%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20men%20in%20the%20world%20would%20play%20out%20on%20rival%20social%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20tweeting%20away%20on%20the%20thing%20many%20of%20us%20still%20call%20Twitter%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20owns%2C%20of%20course%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Trump%20is%20firing%20back%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-technology-group-truth-social%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETruth%20Social%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20would-be%20Twitter%20rival%20he%20owns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20the%20spectacle%20of%20two%20billionaires%20having%20a%20potentially%20deeply%20consequential%20flame%20war%20is%20%E2%80%A6%20truly%20something.%20When%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-dorsey-twitter-creator-billionaire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJack%20Dorsey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20crew%20were%20dreaming%20up%20their%20microblogging%20service%20nearly%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20weren't%20dreaming%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20happening%20on%20two%20different%20social%20networks%20is%20also%20fascinating.%20And%20it%20underscores%20that%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20networks%26quot%3B%20isn't%20always%20the%20best%20way%20to%20think%20about%20these%20platforms.%20At%20least%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20mega-rich%2C%20mega-wealthy%20owners%2C%20these%20things%20are%20simply%20megaphones%20to%20holler%20at%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recall%2C%20became%20a%20surprisingly%20effective%20Twitter%20troll%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20his%20first%20election%2C%20and%20especially%20once%20he%20took%20office.%20He%20became%20expert%20at%20%26quot%3Bprogramming%26quot%3B%20the%20news%20by%20tapping%20out%20a%20few%20incendiary%20lines%20on%20his%20Twitter%20account%2C%20and%20reveling%20in%20the%20chaos%20that%20could%20create.%20(The%20guy%20typing%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fhavoc-on-the-platform-and-off%2Fid1465767420%3Fi%3D1000634111462%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20a%20pretty%20good%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20all%20that.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Twitter%20banned%20Trump%2C%20which%20by%20all%20accounts%20deeply%20upset%20Trump%2C%20and%20that%20banishment%20helped%20prompt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20to%20buy%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20then%20reinstate%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231187d7b-d150-4f36-9f64-68032e82eaa1%5C%22%3EWhy%20Trump%20never%20really%20came%20back%20to%20Twitter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20Trump%20had%20created%20his%20own%20Truth%20Social%20network%20as%20a%20Twitter%20alternative.%20And%20Trump%20has%20both%20a%20legal%20obligation%20and%20a%20financial%20imperative%20to%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fix%3Fdoc%3D%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F0001849635%2F000114036125004822%2Fef20039039_10k.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20license%20agreement%20with%20Trump%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20that%20owns%20Truth%20Social%2C%20requires%20Trump%20to%20post%20all%20%26quot%3Bnon-political%20social%20media%26quot%3B%20items%20to%20Truth%20Social%20first%2C%20then%20wait%20six%20hours%20before%20running%20them%20anywhere%20else.%20More%20important%3A%20If%20the%20guy%20who%20owns%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20isn't%20using%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20for%20his%20social%20media%2C%20why%20would%20anyone%20else%20use%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-donation-donald-trump-still-no-tweet-x-twitter-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEven%20after%20Musk%20and%20Trump%20merged%20forces%20last%20summer%2C%20Trump%20still%20spent%20almost%20no%20time%20on%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20he's%20kept%20plugging%20away%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20what's%20happened%20since%20%E2%80%94%20and%20especially%20now%20%E2%80%94%20forces%20us%20to%20rethink%20how%20these%20platforms%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%3A%20Lots%20of%20people%20who%20used%20to%20use%20the%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%20thought%20that%20removing%20Trump%20from%20Twitter%20would%20diminish%20his%20power.%20But%20that%20obviously%20wasn't%20true.%20Trump%20crushed%20all%20comers%20in%20the%20last%20Republican%20primary%2C%20and%20won%20a%20meaningful%20victory%20in%20last%20fall's%20general%20election%2C%20despite%20little-to-no%20presence%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20important%20is%20that%20Trump's%20ability%20to%20make%20the%20world%20turn%20based%20on%20his%20words%20isn't%20dependent%20on%20Twitter%20at%20all.%20He's%20the%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20so%20whatever%20he%20says%2C%20whenever%20he%20says%20it%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%2C%20on%20the%20White%20House%20lawn%2C%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20%E2%80%94%20gets%20instantly%20amplified%2C%20oftentimes%20with%20great%20consequence.%20Trump%20could%20spout%20off%20on%20Tumblr%20or%20Friendster%20(I%20just%20Googled%20%E2%80%94%20Friendster%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffriendster.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexists%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20his%20message%20would%20get%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20posts%20on%20their%20respective%20platforms%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6842070f9b2a601d01b26e0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222907%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20broke%20up%2C%20in%20real-time%2C%20on%20their%20own%20social%20media%20platforms.%3Cp%3EJakub%20Porzycki%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Trump's%20presence%20on%20Truth%20Social%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20have%20meaningfully%20boosted%20usage%20on%20that%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can't%20measure%20that%20with%20traditional%20metrics%20%E2%80%94%20because%2C%20tellingly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-truth-social-users-disclose-financials-djt-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20Media%20continues%20to%20not%20provide%20any%20metrics%20about%20how%20many%20people%20use%20the%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20on%20vibes.%20You%20may%20read%20plenty%20of%20stories%20about%20how%20Trump%20posted%20something%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20but%20what%20about%20anyone%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20things%20we%20can%20see%20from%20Trump%20Media%20don't%20suggest%20the%20platform%20is%20booming%3A%20In%202024%2C%20the%20company's%20meager%20revenue%20line%20actually%20declined%20by%2012%25%20over%20the%20previous%20year.%20Even%20more%20telling%20may%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdjt-stock-price-trump-media-bitcoin-cryptocurrency-truth-social-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company's%20seeming%20pivot%20into%20life%20as%20a%20bitcoin%20repository%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20Trump%20and%20his%20partners%2C%20but%20doesn't%20suggest%20a%20real%20interest%20in%20running%20a%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20Trump-less%20Twitter%20has%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20thrived%20is%20the%20right%20word.%20A%20meaningful%20number%20of%20influential%20users%20and%20big%20advertisers%20have%20left%20the%20service%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-02-20%2Fbehind-musk-s-x-turnaround-pick-and-choose-financials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20financial%20condition%20seems%20hopeful%20at%20best%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20rise%20of%20would-be%20challengers%2C%20Twitter%20remains%20the%20most%20prominent%20place%20for%20public%2C%20real-time%20chatter%2C%20more%20or%20less%20by%20default.%20That's%20why%20people%20who%20tell%20you%20social%20media%20isn't%20great%20for%20you%20still%20use%20Twitter%20when%20they%20want%20to%20insert%20themselves%20into%20the%20conversation%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-twitter-ezra-klein-elon-musk-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times'%20Ezra%20Klein%20did%20last%20year%20during%20crucial%20points%20in%20the%20election%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20speaks%20to%20the%20stickiness%20of%20social%20networks%2C%20and%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20replicate%20them%20somewhere%20else.%20But%20again%2C%20that%20isn't%20relevant%20to%20Musk's%20use%20of%20the%20platform%20to%20attack%20Trump%3A%20Musk%20could%20print%20out%20all%20of%20his%20insults%20on%20paper%20and%20they'd%20still%20carry%20the%20same%20weight%20and%20import.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4278191-7381-4b2e-b89e-cb26eaf702bd%5C%22%3EWhen%20mega-billionaires%20speak%2C%20people%20listen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20it%20another%20way%3A%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20owns%20multiple%20huge%20social%20networks.%20If%20he%20were%20going%20to%20join%20this%20brawl%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20matter%20which%20one%20of%20them%20he%20used%20to%20come%20over%20the%20top%20rope.%20All%20that%20would%20matter%20is%20the%20world's%20second-richest%20man%20was%20in%20the%20fight%2C%20too%2C%20and%20anything%20he%20said%20or%20did%20would%20be%20covered%20by%20everyone%2C%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20cut%20to%20Thursday%2C%20when%20Trump%20has%20been%20calling%20to%20cut%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114632206992330264%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBillions%20and%20Billions%20of%20Dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20federal%20budget%20by%20%26quot%3Bterminat%5Bing%5D%20Elon's%20Governmental%20Subsidies%20and%20Contracts%26quot%3B%20and%20Musk%20is%20accusing%20Trump%20of%20suppressing%20embarrassing%20information%20about%20disgraced%20financier%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20because%20Trump%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114632206992330264%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20in%20the%20Epstein%20files%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20insults%20and%20threats%20are%20being%20lobbed%20from%20different%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20at%20the%20same%20time%20directly%20responding%20to%20each%20other%20but%20also%20pretending%20the%20other%20one%20doesn't%20exist.%20Like%20exes%20who%20refuse%20to%20speak%20with%20each%20other%2C%20but%20spend%20all%20their%20time%20telling%20their%20mutual%20friends%20how%20awful%20the%20other%20one%20is%2C%20knowing%20it%20will%20get%20back%20directly%20to%20the%20person%20they're%20complaining%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20exes%20are%20two%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20people%20in%20the%20world.%20So%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20platform%20they%20use%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-twitter-x-truth-social-platform-power-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749159307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6842038a9d73a0031e8dfd33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-twitter-x-truth-social-platform-power