ld%2Fus%2Ftrumpmusk-rift-deepens-elon-musk-announces-decommissioning-of-spacex-dragon-spacecraft-after-trump-targets-government-contracts%2Farticleshow%2F121659207.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrumpmusk-rift-deepens-elon-musk-announces-decommissioning-of-spacex-dragon-spacecraft-after-trump-targets-government-contracts%2Famp_articleshow%2F121659207.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrumpmusk-rift-deepens-elon-musk-announces-decommissioning-of-spacex-dragon-spacecraft-after-trump-targets-government-contracts%2Famp_articleshow%2F121659207.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jamie%20Dimon%20just%20made%20good%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20bankers%20with%20hush-hush%20private%20equity%20jobs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20walking%20outside%20the%20JPMorgan%20headquarters%20in%20Manhattan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ffefaae09223df2badd59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOutside%20the%20JPMorgan%20headquarters%20in%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJamie%20Dimon%20has%20criticized%20the%20private%20equity%20industry's%20recruiting%20of%20its%20junior%20bankers.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20firm%20warned%20incoming%20juniors%20not%20to%20accept%20future-dated%20jobs%20from%20buyout%20firms.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThose%20who%20do%20will%20be%20terminated%2C%20the%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20memo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20is%20warning%20junior%20bankers%20against%20taking%20future-dated%20jobs%20with%20buyout%20firms%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20even%20sneaking%20out%20of%20job%20training%20to%20take%20interviews.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20JPMorgan%20Chase's%20top%20investment%20banking%20brass%20sent%20a%20memo%20to%20incoming%20first-year%20IB%20analysts%20warning%20them%20against%20participating%20in%20the%20private%20equity%20industry's%20annual%20recruiting%20ritual%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20whirlwind%20affair%20is%20known%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-recruiting-on-cycle-prepare-career-jamie-dimon-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3Bon-cycle%20recruiting%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20promises%20young%20bankers%20lucrative%20jobs%20at%20the%20end%20of%20their%20investment%20banking%20analyst%20programs%2C%20which%20often%20last%20two%20or%20three%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20memo%2C%20John%20Simmons%20and%20Filippo%20Gori%2C%20co-heads%20of%20global%20banking%2C%20admonished%20analysts%20who%20accept%20%26quot%3Bfuture-dated%20job%20offer%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Ba%20position%20with%20another%20company%20before%20joining%20us%26quot%3B%20within%20their%20first%2018%20months%20of%20employment%2C%20saying%20they%20will%20be%20terminated%20if%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20be%20provided%20notice%20and%20your%20employment%20with%20the%20firm%20will%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20executives%20wrote.%20They%20said%20such%20offers%20could%20constitute%20a%20conflict%20for%20junior%20bankers%20working%20on%20transactions%20for%20PE%20sponsors%20who%20could%20also%20be%20their%20future%20employers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20memo%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20escalation%20of%20a%20long-simmering%20personnel%20issue%20important%20to%20the%20bank's%20high-profile%20CEO%2C%20Jamie%20Dimon.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20unethical.%20I%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20and%20I%20may%20eliminate%20it%20regardless%20of%20what%20the%20private-equity%20guys%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-junior-bankers-private-equity-jobs-unethical-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etold%20college%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20firm%20warned%20incoming%20junior%20bankers%20against%20the%20practice%2C%20but%20stopped%20short%20of%20saying%20it%20would%20terminate%20those%20who%20participated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20memo%20even%20vowed%20to%20terminate%20junior%20bankers%20who%20dare%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-recruitment-process-has-junior-bankers-freaking-out-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esneak%20out%20of%20job%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20interview%20with%20private%20equity%20firms%2C%20as%20many%20did%20in%202023.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20succeed%20in%20the%20Investment%20Banking%20Analyst%20Program%2C%20your%20full%20attention%20and%20participation%20are%20essential%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Simmons%20and%20Gori.%20%26quot%3BAttendance%20at%20all%20training%20sessions%2C%20meetings%20and%20obligations%20is%20required.%20Missing%20any%20part%20of%20the%20training%20program%20may%20lead%20to%20removal%20from%20the%20program%20and%20termination%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20was%20first%20reported%20by%20ExecSum%2C%20a%20newsletter%20offshoot%20of%20the%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flitquidity-anonymous-wall-street-meme-account-identity-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInstagram%20account%20Litquidity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20JPMorgan%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20its%20authenticity%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20has%20previously%20reported%2C%20private%20equity's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-recruiting-on-cycle-timeline-coffee-chats-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eannual%20recruiting%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20junior%20bankers%20is%20a%20frenetic%20affair%20that%20often%20starts%20without%20warning.%20Young%20bankers%20can%20be%20asked%20to%20drop%20everything%20to%20interview%20or%20miss%20out%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0resulting%20in%20middle-of-the-night%20interviews%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhave-private-equity-recruiting-tactics-gone-too-far-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emissed%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20proving%20a%20nagging%20source%20of%20disruption%20for%20bank%20bosses.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20has%20railed%20against%20PE%20recruiting%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20his%20staff.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20wrong%20to%20put%20you%20in%20the%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20kind%20of%20decide%20the%20next%20career%20move%20before%20you%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20even%20decide%20what%20the%20company%20is%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20this%20new%20rule%20could%20impact%20the%20future%20of%20buyside%20recruiting.%20The%20industry%20insiders%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20expressed%20skepticism%20over%20the%20bank's%20ability%20to%20enforce%20the%20new%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20imagine%20while%20some%20junior%20bankers%20will%20be%20scared%20off%2C%20many%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20the%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthony%20Keizner%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20headhunting%20firm%20Odyssey%20Search%20Partners%2C%20told%20BI%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BThey%20always%20saw%20banking%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%2C%20and%20won't%20want%20to%20be%20put%20off%20starting%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20their%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20junior%20banker%20who%20now%20works%20in%20private%20equity%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnalysts%20are%20going%20to%20recruit%20regardless%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20young%20bankers%20will%20simply%20%26quot%3Bshut%20their%20mouths%20about%26quot%3B%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20