ghting%20Apple%20over%20its%20app%20store%20fees%20for%20years.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Luna%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEpic%20Games%20CEO%20Tim%20Sweeney%20celebrated%20his%20court%20victory%20against%20Apple%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESweeney%20was%20locked%20in%20a%20yearslong%20court%20battle%20with%20Apple%20over%20its%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-court-ruling-epic-game-charges-2025-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520a%2520nutshell%3A%2520Epic%2520doesn%2Cled%2520to%2520the%2520civil%2520suit.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApp%20Store%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20says%20it%20plans%20to%20appeal%20the%20decision%20but%20will%20comply%20with%20the%20court's%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Sweeney%20won%2C%20and%20he's%20out%20celebrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20five-year%20battle%20with%20Apple%2C%20Sweeney%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Epic%20Games%2C%20won%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-court-ruling-epic-game-charges-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emassive%20victory%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20court%20last%20month.%20Apple%20must%20tear%20down%20its%20proverbial%20walled%20garden%20and%20allow%20for%20more%20competition%20and%20payment%20methods%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApp%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20take%20a%2027%25%20fee%20from%20US%20developers%20who%20direct%20users%20to%20make%20purchases%20externally.%20And%20that%20means%20that%20Epic's%20popular%20game%2C%20Fortnite%2C%20is%20coming%20back%20to%20iOS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple's%20stay%20is%20denied%20by%20the%209th%20Circuit%20Court.%20The%20long%20national%20nightmare%20of%20the%20Apple%20tax%20is%20ended%2C%26quot%3B%20Sweeney%20said%20on%20X%20on%20Wednesd