vices%2C%20physical%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20and%20in-app%20advertising%20%E2%80%94%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20since%202019%2C%20according%20to%20Apple.%20Spending%20on%20in-app%20advertising%2C%20especially%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Bhelped%20keep%20many%20apps%20free%20or%20low-cost%20for%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweeney%2C%20however%2C%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20a%20new%2C%20more%20egalitarian%20era%20for%20the%20App%20Store%2C%20and%20anticipates%20two%20levels%20of%20change.%20The%20first%2C%20as%20he%20described%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-sweeeney-epic-games-apple-app-store-interview-peter-kafka-2025-05%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBI's%20Peter%20Kafka%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20will%20be%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20users%20are%20free%20to%20learn%20about%20better%20deals%20from%20all%20developers%2C%20and%20all%20developers%20are%20free%20to%20not%20just%20accept%20payments%20outside%20of%20the%20app%20on%20the%20web%2C%20but%20to%20tell%20users%20about%20those%20alternative%20ways%20to%20pay%20and%20to%20give%20consumers%20better%20deals.%20That's%20a%20key%20economic%20gain%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20that%20%26quot%3BApple%20would%20step%20up%20and%20compete%2C%20give%20developers%20a%20much%20better%20deal%20than%2030%25%2C%20and%20actually%20engage%20in%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-sweeney-epic-games-apple-app-store-court-battle-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749151543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841e80ac19ab3675c10bef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-sweeney-epic-games-apple-app-store-court-battle-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Epic%20Games%20CEO%20Tim%20Sweeney%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20a%2