nges%20to%20generative%20AI%20in%20radiology%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHinton's%20notion%20wasn't%20entirely%20off-base.%20Many%20radiologists%20now%20have%20access%20to%20predictive%20AI%20models%20that%20classify%20images%20or%20highlight%20potential%20abnormalities.%20Langlotz%20said%20the%20rise%20of%20these%20tools%20%26quot%3Bcreated%20an%20industry%26quot%3B%20of%20more%20than%20100%20companies%20that%20focus%20on%20AI%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fge-healthcare-ai-clinical-support-medical-imaging-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedical%20imaging%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fmedical-devices%2Fsoftware-medical-device-samd%2Fartificial-intelligence-and-machine-learning-aiml-enabled-medical-devices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20FDA%20lists%20over%201%2C000%20AI%2FML-enabled%20medical%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20include%20algorithms%20and%20software%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20which%20were%20designed%20for%20radiology.%20However%2C%20the%20approved%20devices%20are%20based%20on%20more%20traditional%20machine%20learning%20techniques%2C%20not%20on%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnkur%20Sharma%2C%20the%20head%20of%20medical%20affairs%20for%20medical%20devices%20and%20radiology%20at%20Bayer%2C%20explained%20that%20AI%20tools%20used%20for%20radiology%20are%20categorized%20within%20computer-aided%20detection%20software%2C%20which%20helps%20analyze%20and%20interpret%20medical%20images.%20Examples%20include%20triage%2C%20detection%2C%20and%20characterization.%20Each%20tool%20must%20meet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fregulatory-information%2Fsearch-fda-guidance-documents%2Fcomputer-assisted-detection-devices-applied-radiology-images-and-radiology-device-data-premarket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulatory%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20include%20studies%20to%20determine%20detection%20accuracy%20and%20false%20positive%20rate%2C%20among%20other%20metrics.%20This%20is%20especially%20challenging%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-using-ai-bain-survey-roi-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20technologies%2C%20which%20are%20newer%20and%20less%20well%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharacterization%20tools%2C%20which%20analyze%20specific%20abnormalities%20and%20suggest%20what%20they%20might%20be%2C%20face%20the%20highest%20regulatory%20standards%2C%20as%20both%20false%20positives%20and%20negatives%20carry%20risks.%20The%20idea%20of%20a%20kind%20of%20gen%20AI%20radiologist%20capable%20of%20automated%20diagnosis%2C%20as%20Hinton%20envisioned%2C%20would%20be%20categorized%20as%20%26quot%3Bcharacterization%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20have%20to%20meet%20a%20high%20standard%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulation%20isn't%20the%20only%20hurdle%20generative%20AI%20must%20leap%20to%20see%20broader%20use%20in%20radiology%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday's%20best%20general-purpose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20OpenAI's%20GPT4.1%2C%20are%20trained%20on%20trillions%20of%20tokens%20of%20data.%20Scaling%20the%20model%20in%20this%20way%20has%20led%20to%20superb%20results%2C%20as%20new%20LLMs%20consistently%20beat%20older%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraining%20a%20generative%20AI%20model%20for%20radiology%20at%20this%20scale%20is%20difficult%2C%20however%2C%20because%20the%20volume%20of%20training%20data%20available%20is%20much%20smaller.%20Medical%20organizations%20also%20lack%20access%20to%20compute%20resources%20sufficient%20to%20build%20models%20at%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20largest%20large%20language%20models%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-funding-talks-ai-race-survival-expensive-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20to%20train%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20size%20of%20the%20training%20data%20used%20to%20train%20the%20largest%20text%20or%20language%20model%20inside%20medicine%2C%20versus%20outside%20medicine%2C%20shows%20a%20one-hundred-times%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Langlotz.%20The%20largest%20LLMs%20train%20on%20databases%20that%20scrape%20nearly%20the%20entire%20internet%3B%20medical%20models%20are%20limited%20to%20whatever%20images%20and%20data%20an%20institution%20has%20access%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227949f66d-3fbd-478c-ad35-82d1274d9b3a%5C%22%3EGenerative%20AI's%20current%20reality%20in%20radiology%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20regulatory%20obstacles%20would%20seem%20to%20cast%20doubt%20on%20generative%20AI's%20usefulness%20in%20radiology%2C%20particularly%20in%20making%20diagnostic%20decisions.%20However%2C%20radiologists%20are%20finding%20the%20technology%20helpful%20in%20their%20workflows%2C%20as%20it%20can%20undertake%20some%20of%20their%20daily%20labor-intensive%20administrative%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Sharma%20said%2C%20some%20tools%20can%20take%20notes%20as%20radiologists%20dictate%20their%20observations%20of%20medical%20images%2C%20which%20helps%20with%20writing%20reports.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-notetaker-work-meetings-tech-save-time-boost-efficiency-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20added%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Btaking%20those%20reports%20and%20translating%20them%20into%20more%20patient-friendly%20language.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Langlotz%20said%20a%20product%20that%20drafts%20reports%20can%20give%20radiologists%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20productivity%20advantage.%26quot%3B%20He%20compared%20it%20to%20having%20resident%20trainees%20who%20draft%20reports%20for%20review%2C%20a%20resource%20that's%20often%20available%20in%20academic%20settings%2C%20but%20less%20so%20in%20radiology%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20a%20hospital's%20radiology%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharma%20said%20that%20generative%20AI%20could%20help%20radiologists%20by%20automating%20and%20streamlining%20reporting%2C%20follow-up%20management%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tech-innovations-help-medical-billing-diagnostics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epatient%20communication%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20radiologists%20time%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20their%20%26quot%3Breading%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20includes%20image%20interpretation%20and%20diagnosis%20of%20complex%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20June%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.radai.com%2Fnews%2Fbayer-and-rad-ai-announce-collaboration-agreement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBayer%20and%20Rad%20AI%20announced%20a%20collaboration%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20integrate%20generative%20AI%20reporting%20solutions%20into%20Bayer's%20Calantic%20Digital%20Solution%20Platform%2C%20a%20cloud-hosted%20platform%20for%20deploying%20AI%20tools%20in%20clinical%20settings.%20The%20collaboration%20aims%20to%20use%20Rad%20AI's%20technology%20to%20help%20radiologists%20create%20reports%20more%20efficiently.%20For%20example%2C%20RadAI%20can%20use%20generative%20AI%20transcription%20to%20generate%20written%20reports%20based%20on%20a%20radiologist's%20dictated%20findings.%20Applications%20like%20this%20face%20fewer%20regulatory%20hurdles%20because%20they%20don't%20directly%20influence%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Dr.%20Langlotz%20said%20he%20foresees%20even%20greater%20AI%20adoption%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20will%20be%20a%20change%20in%20radiologists'%20day-to-day%20work%20in%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdi