vironment%2C%20Hulladek%20is%20working%20to%20turn%20a%20crisis%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20They%E2%80%99re%20showing%20that%20what%20we%20throw%20away%20could%20actually%20be%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20cleaner%2C%20more%20sustainable%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20bins%20to%20businesses%3A%20revolutionising%20e-waste%20recycling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%20Recycling%20works%20on%20two%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20directly%20with%20everyday%20households%2C%20and%20in%20partnership%20with%20large%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20B2C%20(Business-to-Consumer)%20model%20brings%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F435253%2Fe-waste-disposal-phones-cords-guide-ngo-cpcb%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-waste%20awareness%20%3C%2Fa%3Eright%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps.%20Through%20regular%2C%20door-to-door%20collection%20drives%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20helping%20families%20understand%20what%20e-waste%20really%20is%2C%20why%20it%20matters%2C%20and%20how%20to%20dispose%20of%20it%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20their%20B2B%20(Business-to-Business)%20arm%20supports%20big%20names%20like%20Godrej%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20Mondelez%20International%2C%20and%20Tata%20Steel.%20Hulladek%20handles%20these%20companies%E2%80%99%20e-waste%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20everything%2C%20from%20data%20destruction%20to%20compliance%20with%20government%20norms%2C%20is%20done%20thoroughly%20and%20transparently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20work%20has%20become%20even%20more%20urgent%20with%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1881761%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProducers%2520of%2520notified%2520EEE%252C%2520have%2Cbeyond%2520the%2520maximum%2520prescribed%2520concentration.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20E-Waste%20(Management)%20Rules%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20in%20place.%20These%20rules%20require%20all%20manufacturers%20of%20electronic%20products%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happens%20to%20their%20products%20after%20use%20%E2%80%94%20a%20principle%20known%20as%20Extended%20Producer%20Responsibility%20(EPR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20companies%20must%20ensure%20their%20e-waste%20is%20being%20collected%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20disposed%20of%20safely%2C%20not%20just%20tossed%20aside.%20The%20law%20also%20sets%20clear%20targets%3A%20by%202023-24%20and%202024-25%2C%2060%25%20of%20e-waste%20generated%20must%20be%20recycled.%20That%20figure%20rises%20to%2070%25%20in%20the%20following%20two%20years%20and%20hits%2080%25%20from%202027-28%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20both%20individuals%20and%20industries%20to%20meet%20these%20goals%2C%20not%20just%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20their%20operation%20model%2C%20Shreya%20Khandelia%2C%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20President%2C%20Recycler%20Relations%20of%20Hulladek%20Recycling%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20initial%20collection%20of%20e-waste%20from%20our%20dedicated%20centres%2C%20the%20materials%20are%20segregated%20and%20sent%20to%20authorised%20recyclers.%20Recycling%20involves%20dismantling%2C%20treating%20hazardous%20components%2C%20and%20segregating%20materials%20into%20categories%20like%20glass%2C%20metal%2C%20and%20plastic%20for%20reuse%20or%20upcycling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20step%20is%20carefully%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20environmental%20standards%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20distinguishes%20us%20from%20informal%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(scrap%20dealers)%2C%20who%20are%20often%20confused%20with%20formal%20recyclers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreya%20says%20what%20makes%20Hulladek%20unique%20is%20not%20just%20its%20mission%20but%20its%20workforce%2C%20which%20is%20predominantly%20led%20by%20women.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20an%20average%20employee%20age%20of%2027%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20be%20innovative%20in%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%2C%20and%20our%20gender%20diversity%20is%20unparalleled%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreya%20beams%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20rooted%20in%20an%20apparent%20belief%3A%20change%20begins%20with%20awareness.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20built%20a%20formidable%20logistics%20network%20backed%20by%20intention%20and%20community%20engagement.%20With%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala%2C%20Hulladek%20conducts%20over%20500%20awareness%20sessions%20each%20year%E2%80%94each%20one%20an%20attempt%20to%20shift%20mindsets%20and%20turn%20passive%20consumers%20into%20conscious%20participants%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20e-waste%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Eastern%20India%2C%20their%20presence%20is%20especially%20significant.%20In%20cities%20like%20Kolkata%2C%20Hulladek%20has%20installed%20nearly%20500%20e-waste%20bins%2C%20not%20just%20as%20collection%20points%20but%20as%20visible%2C%20everyday%20reminders%20that%20electronic%20waste%20is%20real%20and%20needs%20attention.%20These%20bins%2C%20placed%20in%20schools%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20public%20spaces%2C%20have%20become%20quiet%20markers%20of%20a%20larger%20mission%3A%20to%20make%20e-waste%20visible%2C%20understood%2C%20and%20acted%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20a%20smooth%20path.%20The%20road%20to%20awareness%2C%20as%20Priyasha%20Singhania%20shares%2C%20has%20been%20long%20and%20layered.%20%E2%80%9CAwareness%20about%20biodegradable%20and%20non-biodegradable%20waste%20was%20high%2C%20but%20e-waste%20was%20being%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20President%2C%20Branding%20and%20Communication.%20Her%20words%20reflect%20a%20national%20blind%20spot%E2%80%94a%20collective%20unawareness%20of%20the%20toxins%20hiding%20in%20our%20broken%20gadgets%20and%20discarded%20electronics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%201